Movie Description
Secret Service agent Joshua McCord (Chuck Norris), after rescuing the First Lady from terrorist kidnappers, returns to protect the country in a special assignment. This time, the president (Robert Urich) needs McCord to chase down and stop a terrorist who plans to detonate a nuclear weapon in the US!
